    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Observe Peace Process and Constitution Drafting; conduct regional and district observation to track the peace process; track CA and government activity; issue regular reports to raise awareness; engage with national and local political leaders to address political challenges; conduct regular briefings with international stakeholders; coordinate closely with national stakeholders; communicate national findings to local level.\r\n\r\n\tConduct a limited observation of voter registration; deploy existing observation teams to observe voter registration, hire short-term expert consultants to assist and collaborate with the ECN, UNDP, IFES, domestic observer networks and civil society organizations.'\r\n\r\n\tCA Election observation 2013."
      },
